<b>Who can Join:</b><br />
Any individual or entity (e.g. business or organization) that seeks to support the mission of the Foundation can join as Affiliate by donating regularly (e.g. monthly or quarterly or yearly) 20% of his/her take-home income to the Foundation. At no time shall affiliate information be shared with or sold to other organizations or groups without the affiliate’s consent.  At the discretion of the board of directors, affiliates may be given endorsement, recognition and media coverage at fundraising activities, clinics, other events or at the Foundation website.
<br /><br />
<b>Privileges:</b><br />
By being an affiliate (i.e. Joining the Foundation), the individual or entity gets the following privileges:<br />
1. Having a user account to login to Bestower Foundation backend to have access to all documents of the Foundation.<br />
2. Free complimentary email something like username@bestower.org   <br />
3. Keep informed with every events and activities of this Foundation, including all financial transactions.<br />
4. Opportunity to give input to projects, activities that this Foundation undertakes.<br />
5. Eligibility to be an officer of the Foundation.<br />
6. Eligiblity to be elected as directors of the foundation upon completing five years of anniversary as affiliates. <br />
<br />
<b>How to Join:</b><br />
Joining the Foundation is a two step process:<br />
1. Send an email to Board of Directors at <a href="mailto:directors@bestower.org">directors@bestower.org</a> stating your intention to join the foundation as affiliates and making a pledge (monthly / quarterly or yearly) of 20% of take-home income along with your First Name, Last Name, Address, Email and Phone. <br />
2. Donate said pledge amount to the Foundation using your favorite method available in <a href="Donate.html">donation page</a>. 
